{"tid":2229873,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"擺酒既話 邊間好食？係咪酒樓實好食過酒店？","createTime":"2020-10-04T16:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T01:39:04.000Z","uid":349054,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"206ff3a55ff2ec39cdeedc40d5df5de4b54c7108","tid":2229873,"uid":349054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"因為老人家話要擺酒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地好鬼傳統 應該要中式<br />\n疫情過左搞<br />\n預16-18圍到<br />\n有無巴絲打去過婚宴覺得d野食好正分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（因為唔想齋個樣好睇野食唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\nBudget預10000-12000一圍到<br />\n（同男朋友一齊出唔想用咁多錢擺）<br />\n<br />\n同埋偷問一下 大家禮金通常比幾多<br />\n（屋企人無特別要求 都唔知點比好）<br />\n<br />\n多謝分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bec2d8c02b3d8279c95e879284028671deb2983","tid":2229873,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"敍福樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b681ea1869d1921b1bfa3f2114b98f33b8b914","tid":2229873,"uid":54833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2bec2d8c02b3d8279c95e879284028671deb2983","tid":2229873,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"敍福樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"已結業"},{"pid":"059e3ef3b84e478f22b132380b908b878c9446b4","tid":2229873,"uid":349054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bec2d8c02b3d8279c95e879284028671deb2983","tid":2229873,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"敍福樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":